flowchart LR
    T[Edge Cache Proxy Request Flow]

    U[Client App / Browser] --> W[Cloudflare Worker<br/>Edge Cache Proxy]

    W -->|Load endpoint + runtime policy| KV[(Config KV<br/>endpoint rules<br/>TTL bands<br/>operator policy)]

    W -->|1. Edge lookup| EC[(Cloudflare Edge Cache<br/>caches.default)]
    EC -->|HIT| U

    EC -->|MISS| R2[(R2 Persistent Cache)]
    R2 -->|R2 HIT| W
    W -->|Respond to client| U
    W -->|Edge write-back| EC

    R2 -->|MISS / STALE| O[(Protected API backend)]
    O -->|Origin response| W

    W -->|Normalize query + derive cache key| K[Canonical Cache Key<br/>+ operator suffix<br/>+ purge-version suffix]
    K --> EC
    K --> R2

    W -->|2xx / 404 write-back| EC
    W -->|Large payload write-back| R2

    W -->|Trace headers + cache outcome metrics| M[(Analytics / Observability)]

    W -->|BYPASS / STRICT_KV_ONLY checks| G[Policy Gate]
    G -->|Blocked| E[412 policy response]
    E --> U
